parameters:
\F[beni_mizugi1]Akane Suzaku: (Hanasaki, spotted...♪ But of all people to be
next to, it's Sumire-san...)
\F[beni_mizugi4]Akane Suzaku: (Somehow... I have to separate them... Hm?)
\F[beni_mizugi3]Akane Suzaku: "What are you two doing?"

\F[beni_mizugi3]\FF[hanasaku_smile]\AA[2]Sakuya: "Oh... As the head of the detective club, it's
concerning, isn't it? This is it, this thing here."
\F[beni_mizugi3]\FF[sumire_angry]\AA[2]Sumire: "What do you think it is, Akane-san?"

\F[beni_mizugi2]Akane Suzaku: (Th-this is...!? Isn't that Lord Clozeal!!
Struggling and caught..!!)

\F[beni_mizugi2]Akane Suzaku: (I-I have to save him...! But I can't reveal
my true identity...!!)
\F[beni_mizugi2]Akane Suzaku: "What could it be... It's like an eel...?"

\F[beni_mizugi2]\FF[sumire_trouble]\AA[2]Sumire: "Exactly. It's like an eel, but it was crawling on
land. Eels are fish that move between freshwater and
seawater, but they breathe through gills, so on land..."

\F[beni_mizugi2]\FF[hanasaku_smile]\AA[2]Sakuya: "Apparently, as long as their body is wet, they can
breathe through their skin. But for a place like this...
It's quite a distance from any river... Could there be a
fish farm around here?"

\F[beni_mizugi2]\FF[hanasaku_smile]\AA[1]Akane Suzaku: "It seems to want to escape... It's pitiful,
so let's let it go..."

\F[beni_mizugi2]\FF[sumire_trouble]\AA[2]Sumire: "If it were an eel... that would be the case, but...
this creature crawled into my skirt."

\F[beni_mizugi2]\FF[hanasaku_smile]\AA[2]Sakuya: "It was a surprise! It came slithering up suddenly,
and before I knew it, I had plunged my face into Sumire-
san's skirt."

\F[beni_mizugi2]\FF[sumire_angry]\AA[2]Sumire: "If it were by accident, that would be fine... But
if it deliberately tried to crawl into my skirt... If that's
its natural behavior..."
\F[beni_mizugi4]\FF[sumire_angry]\AA[1]Akane Suzaku: "So it's not an eel... but 'something else'?"

\F[beni_mizugi4]\FF[sumire_angry]\AA[2]Sumire: "Yes. If my deduction is correct, it might be the
same as yesterday's bat incident. The person caught by this
eel must surely be a phantom thief..."

\F[beni_mizugi4]\FF[hanasaku_trouble]\AA[2]Sakuya: "Eh!? Is that what you mean!? Then that was a close
call..."

\F[beni_mizugi2]\FF[hanasaku_trouble]\AA[1]]Akane Suzaku: (Damn...! She's absolutely right... This is
bad... Everything's been exposed...)

\F[beni_mizugi2]\FF[sumire_angry]\AA[2]Sumire: "That's right. It's undeniable evidence that a new
phantom thief has started to move. There might not be a
moment to spare... Akane-san... Have you noticed anything
unusual around here?"

\F[beni_mizugi2]\FF[sumire_angry]\AA[1]Akane Suzaku: "Since the commotion yesterday... it's been
quiet..."

\F[beni_mizugi2]\FF[hanasaku_trouble]\AA[2]Sakuya: "The fact that you're bringing this up to Akane-chan
means... things must really be urgent, right...?"

\F[beni_mizugi2]\FF[sumire_angry]\AA[2]Sumire: "Yes. We can't afford to be choosy now. We need
Akane-san's cooperation."

\F[beni_mizugi4]\FF[sumire_angry]\AA[1]Akane Suzaku: (Slither~! As if I'd do such a thing...! I
don't want to get in the way of my master... I have to do
something about these two...)

\F[beni_mizugi4]\FF[hanasaku_trouble]\AA[2]Sakuya: "Speaking of which... Oh! Now that I think about it
because of Akane-chan... Nadeshiko has been acting strange,
hasn't she?"

\F[beni_mizugi4]\FF[hanasaku_trouble]\AA[2]Sakuya: "She doesn't usually do this, but she was inviting
friends to the restroom and..."
\F[beni_mizugi4]\FF[hanasaku_trouble]\AA[1]Akane Suzaku: "!!"

\F[beni_mizugi4]\FF[hanasaku_trouble]\AA[2]Sakuya: "Even though she usually has such a composed face...
she was smiling so happily! Just for going to the
restroom...!!"
\F[beni_mizugi4]\FF[hanasaku_trouble]\AA[1]Akane Suzaku: "..."

\F[beni_mizugi3]\FF[hanasaku_trouble]\AA[1]Akane Suzaku: "Sumire-san... If you let go of your hand,
that eel might escape and attack."

\F[beni_mizugi3]\FF[sumire_angry]\AA[2]Sumire: "Yes. That's why I'm holding on tightly. We need to
put it into something from the bag and tie it up or it could
be dangerous."
\F[beni_mizugi4]\FF[sumire_angry]\AA[1]Akane Suzaku: "I won't let you do that though!"
\FF[sumire_angry]Sumire: "!!"
歩行紅
歩行紅

\F[beni_close1]Akane Suzaku: "Slither~♪ If you let go, the Clozeal you're
holding will attack Hanasaki!"

\F[beni_close1]\FF[sumire_trouble]\AA[2]Sumire: "No way!! Akane-san, you've already been turned by
the phantom thief..!!"
\FF[hanasaku_trouble]Sakuya: "I-I didn't notice!! Get away from Sumire-san!!"

\F[beni_close1]\FF[hanasaku_trouble]\AA[1]Akane Suzaku: "Heheh...♪ Did you think there was only one
Clozeal? They're always with us♪"

\F[beni_close1]\FF[sumire_trouble]\AA[2]Sumire: "That's unfair!! If I let go, I can't transform...
Ughh...!! Ackk..!!"
\F[beni_close1]\FF[hanasaku_trouble]\AA[2]Sakuya: "Sumire-san!! What's wrong!!"
\F[beni_close1]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[2]Sumire: "This is bad...!! It's entering me..."
\F[beni_close1]\FF[sumire_trouble]\AA[1]Akane Suzaku: "Slither~♪ Sharing the happiness~♪"
\F[beni_close1]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[2]Sumire: "Aah... Aaah!! It's moving... inside meee♪"
\F[beni_close1]\FF[hanasaku_trouble]\AA[2]Sakuya: "No, stop it!! Akane-chan, please stop...!!"

\F[beni_close1]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[2]Sumire: "Ahfuuh♪ From inside my stomach... I'm being
remadeee♪ The slimy feeling is overflowing from my skin...
I'm fallinggg"
\F[beni_close1]\FF[hanasaku_trouble]\AA[2]Sakuya: "Aah!! Sumire-san..!!"

\F[beni_close1]\FF[hanasaku_trouble]\AA[1]Akane Suzaku: "Slither~♪ Hanasaku... Is it really the time
to worry about others?"
\F[beni_close1]\FF[hanasaku_trouble]\AA[2]Sakuya: "Eh?"
\F[beni_close1]\FF[hanasaku_trouble]\AA[1]Akane Suzaku: "You've already let go♪ Sumire-san"

Sakuya: "Ah... Ahhyaaah!! Ahkuu...!! It's happening to me
toooo♪"
Akane Suzaku: "Let's become friends together, nicely...♪"
Sumire: "The sliminess... Ahhaaahn♪ It feels so goood♪"

Sakuya: "I'm being changed♪ I'm turning into an eel-like
creatureee...♪"

\F[beni_close1]Akane Suzaku: "Slither~♪ You both look so cute now♪ You've
come to love Clozeal-sama, haven't you?"

\F[beni_close1]\FF[sumire_close]\AA[2]Sumire: "Yes, this sliminess is irresistible♪ I feel almost
sorry for having tried to capture it. I should have just
surrendered like this from the start♪"

\F[beni_close1]\FF[hanasaku_close]\AA[2]Sakuya: "That's right. Sumire-san... I'm sorry for
interfering earlier."

\F[beni_close1]\FF[sumire_close]\AA[2]Sumire: "Slither~♪ It's okay. Sakuya-san, you've become one
of us too♪ All's well that ends well."

\F[beni_close1]\FF[sumire_close]\AA[1]Akane Suzaku: "That's right, all's well that ends well. Now
we can attack the members of Iris Blade from behind when we
assault them♪"

\F[beni_close1]\FF[sumire_close]\AA[2]Sumire: "Yes, we'll pretend to fight alongside everyone...
right?"

\F[beni_close1]\FF[hanasaku_close]\AA[2]Sakuya: "It's a bad idea but... nice one♪ Because... it
means we can quickly make Ayaka-chan and the others join us
too♪"
\F[beni_close1]\FF[sumire_close]\AA[2]Sumire: "Fufufufu... I'm looking forward to it♪"
\F[beni_close1]\FF[sumire_close]\AA[1]Akane Suzaku: "Fufufu... So am I...♪"
